If you want Medicare to help you compare drug plans, here are a few suggestions. 1) Have your Medicare card and a list of all your medications handy. BY TELEPHONE Medicare has hired 8,000 people to answer questions about the drug benefit and they are still learning their jobs. The fastest way to talk to a live person is to select ``enrollment.'' When you are ready to talk to a live person, either return to the main menu and start over, or select the ``status'' option and follow that with the ``agent'' option. 